extends _layout 

block content 
	// The form should have 'action=`/functionality/${func._id}/edit` method="GET"' before its class
	div(class="text-gray-900 font-light text-5xl items-center text-center")
		| Add node functionality
		div(class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600")
			| Add a functionality by specifying its name, setup() code and loop() code. The code should be written in Python. 
			| When a functionality is added to a slave node, the master node pushes the code to the specific slave node. 
			| You can use the predefined functions <a class="italic">upload(dict)</a> and <a class="italic">wait(int)</a>. 
			| <a class="font-normal text-semibold text-gray-900">Note: This feature should only be used by super-users.</a>
	div(id="sectionSplitter" class="w-full border-b mb-8 mt-8")
	div(class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center")
		div(class="flex flex-col font-light text-2xl mb-2 font-normal items-center")
			| Name of functionality
			div(id="infoName" class="text-lg font-light mb-4 max-w-xl")
				| Input the name of your new functionality. 
			input(type="name" name="newFuncName" class="text-center shadow px-1 py-2 bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none rounded-lg text-xl mb-4" placeholder="Name")
	div(id="sectionSplitter" class="w-full lg:w-0 border-t mt-4 pt-6 lg:border-none lg:pt-0 lg:mt-2")
	div(class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-around items-center text-xl w-full lg:space-x-12")
		div(id="setupSection" class="width-1/2  text-center")
			div(class="font-light text-2xl mb-2 font-normal")
				| Setup() function
			div(id="infoMaster" class="text-md font-light mb-4 max-w-xl")
				| Input your setup code for the node. The code should be written in Python. 
			div(class="flex justify-center text-3xl mb-6 mt-8 h-48")
				textarea(id="setupFunc" class="text-sm overflow-auto text-gray-900 border-2 border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-2 bg-indigo-100 w-full h-full focus:outline-none" placeholder="some code;")
		div(id="sectionSplitter" class="w-full lg:w-0 border-t mt-4 pt-6 lg:border-none lg:pt-0 lg:mt-0")
		div(id="loopSection" class="width-1/2  text-center")
			div(class="font-light text-2xl mb-2 font-normal")
				| Loop() function
			div(id="infoSlave" class="text-md font-light mb-4 max-w-xl")
				| Input your loop code for the node. The code should be written in Python. 
			div(class="flex justify-center text-3xl mb-6 mt-8 h-48")
				textarea(id="loopFunc" class="text-sm text-gray-900 overflow-auto border-2 border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-2 bg-indigo-100 w-full h-full focus:outline-none" placeholder="some code;")
	form(class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-4")
		button(type="submit" class="shadow text-3xl place-self-center px-8 py-1 bg-teal-300 border border-teal-300 rounded-lg text-indigo-100 hover:border-teal-300 hover:bg-indigo-100 hover:text-teal-300 focus:outline-none") 
			| Add functionality
	
	// *********   Confirm functionality modal (For adding a functionality from 'edit-node' page)   ************
	
	div(id="confirmFunc" class="hidden flex z-10 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-75 absolute inset-0 justify-center items-center text-center")
		div(class="bg-gray-200 max-w-4xl py-3 px-3 rounded-lg shadow-xl")
			div(class="flex text-white")
				<svg id="closeConfirmFunc" class="ml-auto text-gray-700 w-5 h-5 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-300 rounded-full" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
			div(class="flex justify-center")
				img(class="h-16 w-auto mr-2" src='/images/logo.png' alt='Wine logo black')
			div(class="flex justify-center items-center")
				h4(class="text-3xl font-light px-10") Are you sure you want to add this functionality? 
			form(action="" method="POST" class="flex flex-col")
				div(class="flex flex-col font-light text-lg mb-2 font-normal items-center font-light mt-6")
					div(class="mb-2") Functionaloty name
					div(id="infoName" class="text-lg font-light mb-2 max-w-xl")
						input(type="name" name="newFuncName" class="text-center shadow px-1 py-2 bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none rounded-lg text-lg" placeholder="Name")
				div(id="sectionSplitter" class="w-full lg:w-0 mt-2 mb-2 lg:border-none lg:pt-0 lg:mt-0")
				div(class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-evenly items-center text-xl w-full lg:space-x-2")
					div(id="setupSection" class="text-center")
						div(class="font-light text-lg mb-2 font-normal")
							| Setup() function
						div(class="flex justify-center text-3xl mb-2 mt-2 h-48")
							textarea(id="setupFunc" class="text-sm overflow-auto text-gray-900 border-2 border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-2 bg-indigo-100 w-full h-full focus:outline-none" placeholder="some code;")
					div(id="sectionSplitter" class="w-full lg:w-0 mt-2 mb-2 lg:border-none lg:pt-0 lg:mt-0")
					div(id="loopSection" class="text-center")
						div(class="font-light text-lg mb-2 font-normal")
							| Loop() function 
						div(class="flex justify-center text-3xl mb-2 mt-2 h-48")
							textarea(id="loopFunc" class="text-sm text-gray-900 overflow-auto border-2 border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-2 bg-indigo-100 w-full h-full focus:outline-none" placeholder="some code;")
				div(class="mt-6 flex justify-center text-3xl")
					button(type="submit" id="confirmFuncBtn" class="shadow px-8 py-1 bg-indigo-300 border border-indigo-300 rounded-lg text-gray-100 hover:border-indigo-300 hover:bg-gray-200 hover:text-indigo-300 focus:outline-none")
						| Confirm
			div(class="text-xs flex justify-center mt-4 mb-2")
				p Clicking confirm will add the functinality to your functionalities. 

	// *********   Modal ends here   ************